question: I need assistance in locating a Sushi restaurant within 180 kilometers from Atlantic Rehabilitation Institute, Madison, NJ. Can you help me out?
sql:
SELECT * FROM pois
WHERE ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.43567 40.767262)',4326)::geography, 180000)
AND amenity = 'restaurant'
AND cuisine ILIKE '%Sushi%';

answers.opening_hours: Tu-Sa 12:00-20:00 open "Dining In" || Tu-Sa 12:00-19:00 open "App Orders"
